K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-3: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-5: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-6: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po dri ma gsum spangs pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-7: sangs rgyas padma rgyas pa'i 'dab 'dra'i spyan mnga' ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-8: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed dang po 'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-9: de yis nye bar bstan pa'i mchog rab mi g-yo ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-10: 'jig rten gsum na grags shing lha dang mis mchod pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-11: chos kyi dam pa skye dgu rnams la zhi byed pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-12: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gnyis pa 'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-13: dge 'dun dam pa'i chos ldan thos pa'i bkra shis phyug /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-14: mi dang lha dang lha ma yin gyis mchod pa'i gnas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-15: tshogs kyi mchog rab ngo tsha shes dang dpal gyi gzhi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-16: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gsum pa 'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-17: sems can kun la phan phyir byang chub mnga' ba po //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-18: don rnams thams cad 'grub par brtul ba yongs ldan pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-19: tshogs kyi lam gyis thub pa'i bkra shis gang byung ba; ;bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-20: 'gro la phan phyir de bzhin gshegs pa dga' ldan lha'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:365b-21: gzhal med khang gi snying po nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-1: bcas lha yis bskor ba'i bkra shis gang byung ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-2: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams pa zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-3: lo ma me tog 'od 'bar nyams dga' lum b'i'i tshal; ;lha mang dag gis bsten par mgon po bltam pa na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-4: srid pa'i mthar phyin pa yi bkra shis gang byung pa //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-6: grong khyer ser skya'i gnas nas rgyal po'i pho brang du //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-7: lhums nas bltam pa ston pa bde gshegs zas gtsang sras //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-8: myur bskrun bdud rtsi'i chus gtor ba yi bkra shis gang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-10: grong khyer dam pa ser skya'i gnas zhes bya bar ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-11: rmad du grags pa che ba'i lha yis mngon bstod pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-12: bsam pas dge bsgrubs bsod nams phung po'i bkra shis gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-13: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-14: dgyes shing nam phyed grong khyer mchog nas mngon byung ste //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-15: dka' thub tshal du mngon par gshegs shing tshangs la sogs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-16: lha yi tshogs kyis yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-18: rab tu 'od 'bar gser dang 'dra ba'i sku mnga' zhing; ;beed'urya ltar sngo ba'i rtsva bting steng bzhugs te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-19: skyil mo krung bcas mi g-yo mchog gi bkra shis gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366a-20: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-0: chu bo'i @366b 'gram na tsa sha'i phreng gis yongs bskor ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-1: shin tu rmad du byung ba'i srid pa sel mdzad pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-2: klu yi rgyal pos phyag byas pa yi bkra shis gang //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-4: shing rgyal drung gshegs byams pa'i stobs kyis bdud kyi phyogs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-5: mang po btul te sa steng dang ni nam mkha' la //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-8: sdug bsngal mtha' dag gzhig phyir rdo rje'i gdan bzhugs te //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-16: bkra shis gang zhig phan byed dam pa dag byed pa //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-20: mu stegs byed pa kun gyi nga rgyal gzhom pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-21: 'gro la bde ba bskyed phyir cho 'phrul dam pa dag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-22: nye bar ston pa rgyal ba'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:366b-23: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-1: la phan phyir mtho ris nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-2: tshangs pa la sogs lha tshogs lag na rnga yab gdugs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-3: sna tshogs thogs pas yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-4: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-5: de bzhin gshegs pa zhi ba mchog tu nyer gshegs pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-6: man dar ba'i me tog mang pos mngon mchod pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-7: lha mchog rnams kyis mngon par bstod pa'i bkra shis gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-8: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-9: lha dbang klu dang mi yi dbang pos phyag byas pa //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-11: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu ldan pa'i bkra shis gang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-12: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-13: dkon mchog gsum dang mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-14: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-073:367a-15: zhus chen gyi lotstsha ba bande ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o ////
